# Local-only SourceKit/SwiftPM editing aid (VS Code): a symlink to the
# Flutter-generated FlutterFramework SPM package in the example's build output,
# so `swift package resolve` can resolve the plugin package standalone and the
# Swift LSP stops reporting "No such module 'MapLibre'". Machine-local, never
# committed. See README → "Editing the native Swift in VS Code".
FlutterFramework
